♫ <i>I'm flying in the sky</i> ♫

403
00:33:46,839 --> 00:33:54,380
♫ <i>My only wish is your happiness</i> ♫

404
00:34:19,819 --> 00:34:21,219
I...

405
00:34:22,339 --> 00:34:24,039
Now, I...

406
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:28,979
I think it's like a dream.

407
00:34:28,979 --> 00:34:31,740
I can't believe it's real.

408
00:34:34,719 --> 00:34:39,618
From now on, I'm your wife.

409
00:34:39,618 --> 00:34:43,398
We will never leave or abandon each other.

410
00:34:43,398 --> 00:34:45,459
We'll be together till the end.

411
00:34:45,459 --> 00:34:48,959
Dear Wife, I swear to you...

412
00:34:51,420 --> 00:34:53,258
It's the wedding night.

413
00:34:53,259 --> 00:34:56,040
Don't say anything ominous.

414
00:35:01,059 --> 00:35:02,759
I believe in you.

415
00:35:06,259 --> 00:35:11,279
But I have to leave for Dingxiang tomorrow.

416
00:35:11,279 --> 00:35:13,338
You must go.

417
00:35:13,338 --> 00:35:19,839
But promise me, Dear, take care of yourself, protect Changge,

418
00:35:19,839 --> 00:35:23,800
and help Li Jing put down the rebellion.

419
00:35:24,819 --> 00:35:27,720
Father and I, we will be waiting for you.

420
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:29,260
I will.

421
00:35:30,499 --> 00:35:32,500
I'll do everything you want.

422
00:36:01,779 --> 00:36:04,379
- Where's Xu Feng?
- He's getting information.

423
00:36:04,379 --> 00:36:06,798
He can play his strengths everywhere.

424
00:36:06,798 --> 00:36:09,699
I need you to do something urgent and important. Only you can do that.

425
00:36:09,699 --> 00:36:11,099
What?

426
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:14,999
Buy some flour, nuts, and yuk butter. All materials for moon cakes.

427
00:36:14,999 --> 00:36:16,760
And sky lanterns.

428
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:18,800
It's urgent and important?

429
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:21,179
Changge, what are you going to do?

430
00:36:21,179 --> 00:36:22,980
Call our people inside.

431
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:28,398
Young Master. I know why tribe commanders were summoned to the city.

432
00:36:34,140 --> 00:36:35,139
Mimi.

433
00:36:35,140 --> 00:36:36,040
- She'er.
- Why are you here?

434
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:38,219
Bad news. Khatun summoned tribe commanders to the city.

435
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:41,279
Tomorrow, at noon, they'll behead Ashile Sun.

436
00:36:41,279 --> 00:36:43,498
His head will be passed around tribes as a warning.

437
00:36:43,499 --> 00:36:44,999
What?

438
00:36:48,460 --> 00:36:51,619
No. It can't happen.

439
00:36:51,620 --> 00:36:52,738
What are you planning?

440
00:36:52,739 --> 00:36:54,338
You know Khatun well, don't you?

441
00:36:54,339 --> 00:36:57,499
No one can change her decision.

442
00:37:03,299 --> 00:37:04,258
Bad luck gets together.

443
00:37:04,259 --> 00:37:07,179
Who lights sky lanterns today? It's not a holiday.

444
00:37:07,760 --> 00:37:09,160
Mimi.

445
00:37:11,399 --> 00:37:13,959
She'er, do you want to eat moon cakes?

446
00:37:13,959 --> 00:37:15,460
What?

447
00:37:20,299 --> 00:37:22,538
I entrust Great Khan to you, General.

448
00:37:22,539 --> 00:37:23,619
Take it easy.

449
00:37:23,620 --> 00:37:25,859
I have a gentlemen's covenant with Elder Qin.

450
00:37:25,860 --> 00:37:28,538
He'll be safe with me.

451
00:37:28,539 --> 00:37:30,039
Thank you very much.

452
00:37:31,940 --> 00:37:34,000
You're not staying. Where are going to?

453
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:36,878
Mission's completed. I have something private to do.

454
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:53,560
You...

455
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:55,600
Mu Jin, I know it.

456
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:58,700
We're brothers. Why are you leaving us alone?

457
00:37:59,380 --> 00:38:02,219
What? Only you can take responsibility to rescue General?

458
00:38:02,220 --> 00:38:04,099
Right!

459
00:38:04,100 --> 00:38:06,819
You don't trust us, do you?

460
00:38:12,839 --> 00:38:14,339
Follow me!

461
00:38:33,259 --> 00:38:36,179
We've received orders. No one gets out.

462
00:38:36,179 --> 00:38:39,419
Gentlemen, I'm the servant of Young Khan.

463
00:38:39,419 --> 00:38:43,459
He has been having a bad appetite recently and is wanting to eat some moon cakes.

464
00:38:43,460 --> 00:38:47,000
Could you please buy some moon cakes for me?

465
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,679
It's not Mid-Autumn Festival.

466
00:38:48,679 --> 00:38:50,058
Where can I find moon cakes?

467
00:38:50,059 --> 00:38:53,159
Go and you can find them.

468
00:38:55,979 --> 00:39:00,279
If Young Khan can eat moon cakes, Khatun will feel better.

469
00:39:00,279 --> 00:39:04,800
Keep the change for some drinks.

470
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:08,018
Okay, I'll go find it when I take a break.

471
00:39:08,018 --> 00:39:11,441
But if I can't find it, please don't blame me.

472
00:39:11,441 --> 00:39:13,441
Thank you very much.

473
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:18,539
Try another one, please.

474
00:39:18,539 --> 00:39:20,520
This kettle is fine.

475
00:39:22,240 --> 00:39:24,838
Moon cake with mixed nuts.

476
00:39:24,838 --> 00:39:26,759
Fresh moon cakes here.

477
00:39:26,759 --> 00:39:29,240
Moon cake. Mixed nuts.

478
00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:30,460
<i>[Moon Cake]</i>

479
00:39:30,460 --> 00:39:32,720
Moon cake.

480
00:39:32,720 --> 00:39:35,739
Moon cake with mixed nuts.

481
00:39:37,010 --> 00:39:38,068
I want these two.

482
00:39:38,068 --> 00:39:39,769
Sure, sir.

483
00:39:40,810 --> 00:39:42,710
Please take it.

484
00:39:53,929 --> 00:39:56,129
Master.

485
00:39:56,129 --> 00:39:59,849
I'm quicker than you thought, right?

486
00:39:59,849 --> 00:40:02,548
Luo Shiba and I galloped day and night.

487
00:40:02,549 --> 00:40:05,009
Several horses died on the way.

488
00:40:05,670 --> 00:40:09,379
And you, how stupid you are.

489
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:11,610
Do you really think you're invulnerable?

490
00:40:11,610 --> 00:40:13,868
How can you come to Dingxiang alone?

491
00:40:13,869 --> 00:40:15,869
Master.

492
00:40:15,869 --> 00:40:18,889
Luo Shiba has met our guys at the inn.

493
00:40:18,889 --> 00:40:20,548
What should I do?

494
00:40:20,548 --> 00:40:21,949
Tell me now.

495
00:40:21,950 --> 00:40:24,228
It's less than six hours before noon.

496
00:40:24,229 --> 00:40:26,788
Take some people and find Wei Shuyu.

497
00:40:26,789 --> 00:40:29,670
We have a plan.

498
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:31,510
Take care of yourself.

499
00:40:41,289 --> 00:40:43,988
Think about it again. We can leave right now.

500
00:40:43,988 --> 00:40:46,689
- You can pretend to be innocent.
- Where's Li Changge's letter? Give it to me now.

501
00:40:46,689 --> 00:40:49,010
There's not much time left for Sun.

502
00:40:51,050 --> 00:40:54,169
Have you really decided to go against your mother?

503
00:40:54,169 --> 00:40:57,568
No. She's my mother forever.

504
00:40:58,610 --> 00:41:01,429
I just want to mitigate her crime.

505
00:41:24,770 --> 00:41:26,370
She'er.

506
00:41:27,550 --> 00:41:30,250
<i>[Need an accurate map of the palace. Mark the following locations.]</i>

507
00:41:32,710 --> 00:41:34,089
I'll do that.

508
00:41:34,090 --> 00:41:37,708
I'm the Young Khan. It's not difficult for me.

509
00:41:45,050 --> 00:41:48,750
She'er... thank you.

510
00:41:48,750 --> 00:41:52,320
I said I'm mitigating a crime for my mother.

511
00:41:53,259 --> 00:41:56,260
I don't want to see Sun dying in front of me.

512
00:42:12,220 --> 00:42:15,559
Young Master, what are you waiting for?

513
00:42:15,559 --> 00:42:17,860
Ashile Sun will be beheaded in a minute.

514
00:42:17,860 --> 00:42:21,678
We're waiting for a map, telling us where the execution platform is,

515
